  <brief_title>Comparison of Single Intravitreal Injection of Triamcinolone or Bevacizumab for the Treatment of Diabetic Macular Edema</brief_title>
  <acronym>Tribeva-DME</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 2 Study of Comparison of Single Intravitreal Injection of Triamcinolone or Bevacizumab for the Treatment of Diabetic Macular Edema.</official_title>
